Month: The specific month in Q2 2024 for which the call volume is recorded. Helps track trends over the quarter.
Average_Call_Volume: The average number of customer service calls received in a month. Useful for assessing call center load and resource allocation.
Chatbot_Interactions: Number of interactions handled by the chatbot, indicating its usage relative to call volume.
Potential_Cost_Savings: Estimated cost savings from using chatbots instead of live agents for handling service calls.
Call_Volume_Change_Percentage: The percentage change in call volume compared to the previous month, indicating trends or anomalies.
